{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/90744", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/90744/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/90744/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/90744/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/90744", "id": 1049233381, "node_id": "I_kwDOAAsO6M4-igfl", "number": 90744, "title": "[ER] NonZeroUX::pow()", "user": {"login": "leonardo-m", "id": 22328461, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjIyMzI4NDYx", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/22328461?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/leonardo-m", "html_url": "https://github.com/leonardo-m", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/leonardo-m/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/leonardo-m/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/leonardo-m/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/leonardo-m/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/leonardo-m/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/leonardo-m/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/leonardo-m/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/leonardo-m/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/leonardo-m/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 5, "created_at": "2021-11-09T23:27:39Z", "updated_at": "2021-11-10T08:43:10Z", "closed_at": "2021-11-10T08:43:10Z", "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "Currently rustc (1.58.0-nightly 2021-11-08) compiles this with a division by zero test:\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nfn foo1(x: u64, y: u32) -> u64 {\r\n    x / 6_u64.pow(y)\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nWhen the base isn't zero and there isn't an overflow base^exp shoudn't be zero. I think currently this can't be solved adding an assume() before the return inside the pow() function because base could be zero.\r\n\r\nTo solve this problem I suggest to add the pow() method to NonZeroUX values:\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nfn foo2(x: u64, y: u32) -> u64 {\r\n    x / NonZeroU64::new(6).unwrap().pow(y)\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nA pow() for NonZeroUX could be something like:\r\n\r\n```rust\r\n#![feature(const_option)]\r\nuse std::num::NonZeroU64;\r\n\r\nconst fn pow(x: NonZeroU64, mut n: u32) -> NonZeroU64 {\r\n    let mut x = x.get();\r\n    if n == 0 {\r\n        return NonZeroU64::new(1).unwrap();\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    let mut y = 1;\r\n    while n > 1 {\r\n        if n & 1 != 0 {\r\n            y *= x;\r\n            n -= 1;\r\n        }\r\n        x *= x;\r\n        n >>= 1;\r\n    }\r\n    unsafe { NonZeroU64::new_unchecked(y * x) }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n(LLVM is able to totally elide at compile-time the unwrap from NonZeroU64::new(1).unwrap() and NonZeroU64::new(6).unwrap()).", "closed_by": {"login": "leonardo-m", "id": 22328461, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjIyMzI4NDYx", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/22328461?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/leonardo-m", "html_url": "https://github.com/leonardo-m", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/leonardo-m/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/leonardo-m/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/leonardo-m/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/leonardo-m/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/leonardo-m/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/leonardo-m/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/leonardo-m/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/leonardo-m/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/leonardo-m/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/90744/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/90744/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": "completed"}